  "title": "Round Trees",
  "description": "Trees are round in real life, why aren't they in Minecraft?",
  "body": "<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Trees are <strong>round</strong> in real life – why aren't they in Minecraft? Well, I created a pack aiming to solve this issue!</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">You can finally rest in peace knowing your trees are as round as they should be.</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Fully compatible with other resourcepacks, just make sure you put Round Trees on top of the order!</span></p>\n<img alt=\"A huge round oak tree overlooking forests full of other round trees\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/XlqZTP4W/images/ae36e495ff5454c55249e1bbdec7930c417dcb84.webp\"/>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/f4eb3536092ffc67ba61236a96a7115a44f65098.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"842\" height=\"219\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">You want Bushy Leaves? Check out the companion pack, <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/better-leaves\">Motschen's Better Leaves.</a></span></p>\n<a title=\"Round Trees Project Page\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/better-leaves\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/ff62e782ee2fbe5fec71a7c14ac5f38a4f350f07.png\" alt=\"Better Leaves Logo\" width=\"496\" height=\"129\" /></a>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<details>\n<summary>Explicitly supported Mods (v8.0):</summary>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/ad-astra\">Ad Astra</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/architects-palette\">Architect's Palette</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"\">Atmospheric</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/aurorasdecorations\">Aurora's Decorations</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"\">Autumnity</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/betterend\">Better End</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/betternether\">Better Nether</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/bewitchment\">Bewitchment</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/biome-makeover\">Biome Makeover</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/biomes-o-plenty\">Biomes O' Plenty</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"\">Blockus</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/blossom\">Blossom</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"\">Botania</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"\">Chipped</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"\">Cluttered</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cobblemon\">Cobblemon</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://curseforge.com/mod/croptopia\">Croptopia</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"\">Cultural Delights</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/deeperdarker\">Deeper and Darker</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/ecologics\">Ecologics</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/ends-phantasm\">End's Phantasm</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/environmental\">Environmental</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"\">Fortuituous Feasts</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"\">Hellion's Sniffer+</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"\">Hibernal Herbs</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/lets-do-beachparty\">[Let's Do] Beachparty</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/lets-do-blooming-nature\">[Let's Do] Blooming Nature</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/lets-do-meadow\">[Let's Do] Meadow</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/lets-do-vinery\">[Let's Do] Vinery</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/natures-spirit\">Nature's Spirit</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/nethers-exoticism\">Nether's Exoticism</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/mariposa\">Mariposa</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/oh-the-biomes-weve-gone\">Oh The Biomes We've Gone</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/paradise-lost\">Paradise Lost</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"\">Promenade</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://m